name: DreamerDAO
description:
This project is to fund for launching a virtual concert in the metaverse for Michael Jackson with the purpose of appealing for peace and love, meanhile , it will also be used for NFT production and public goods .As a return , the contributors will get $DM governance tokens proportionally and also one NFT airdrop designed by the renowned artists if donate more than 0.1 ETH.
This project is co-sponsored by the World Peace Artists Union and Dreamerdao, including 500 famous artists around the world , some of their artworks were almost sold up to millions of dollars for each piece ,the NFT series will be designed by those artists together. In future, Dreamdao will build its own NFT platform to benefit the artists & players with a competitive mechnisam.
